tweet: I commend our brave US military forces for the successful raid in northwest Syria on Saturday which killed the world’s most wanted terrorist, ISIS leader Abu Bakr al-Baghdadi. We must continue to be vigilant in our efforts to fight terrorism and defend our national security.
Rep. Cook Statement on Impeachment: https://bit.ly/30Zgyf3

For two decades, Kurds have fought on frontlines alongside US troops against terror. We should remain in a position to prevent unnecessary conflict between two of our traditional allies. Abandoning the Kurds could lead to devastating loss of life and the potential return of ISIS.
